MP3::M3U::Parser
================

Parses M3U mp3 playlists and if wanted, exports the parsed data to 
formats like xml and html.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

	File::Spec
	IO::File
	Cwd
	Text::Template

All are available on CPAN

